title: Edmund Kemper III - Wannabe Cop Turns Deadly
description:
Hi Friends!

Hope you are having a wonderful day today. Today I wanted to talk about Edmund Kemper III. Isn’t it kind of strange how most of these people we have been talking about have very similar names? What's that all about? Anyways, the dude was a problem. Really, that’s what we can say about him.
 
Please be safe out there, try and make some good choices! I love and appreciate you all so much and I will be seeing you very very soon.

xo
Bailey Sarian

Check out the original video here and don't forget to subscribe to my YouTube @BaileySarian!
